item.title: CVE-2018-3952|2024-09-16T17:28:50.687Z -- talos -- nordvpn
item.description: An exploitable code execution vulnerability exists in the connect functionality of NordVPN 6.14.28.0. A specially crafted configuration file can cause a privilege escalation, resulting in the execution of arbitrary commands with system privileges.
